<H3> <TI>   Maung Maung Khin Receives Malaysian Minister </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Maung Maung Khin Receives Malaysian Minister </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2706155194 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 27 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2706155194 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>
<F P=105>  Burmese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Visiting Malaysian Primary Industries Minister 
Datuk Sri Dr. Lim Keng Yaik and delegation paid a courtesy call 
on Vice Admiral Maung Maung Khin, member of the State Law and 
Order Restoration Council [SLORC] and deputy prime minister, at 
the latter's office at 0930 this morning. 
  At the meeting, cordial and frank talks were held on 
improving bilateral goodwill relations and economic cooperation, 
including foreign investment matters. 
  Also present at the meeting were Brigadier General Abel, 
minister of national planning and economic development; 
responsible personnel, and Mr. John Tenewi Nuek, ambassador of 
Malaysia. 

