South side area at Panmunjom at 1000 [0100 GMT] on 28 June. 
  Kim Yong-sun, chairman of the Reunification Policy Committee 
of the Supreme People's Assembly and head of our delegation; An 
Pyong- su, vice chairman of the Committee for the Peaceful 
